{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01MHgym5RnB8s2qUH7EZDgyL","type":"tool_result","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Perfect. Now let me create a comprehensive summary of the E2E local test infrastructure exploration.\n\n## Exploration Complete\n\nI've thoroughly examined the E2E local test infrastructure for the platform app. Here's a comprehensive report of what I found:\n\n---\n\n## **1. Local E2E Configuration**\n\n**File:** `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/playwright.local.config.ts`\n\nConfiguration highlights:\n- **Test directory:** `./e2e` with pattern matching `local/**/*.spec.ts`\n- **Execution mode:** Single worker, no parallel tests (fully parallel disabled)\n- **Server:** Vite dev server on port 3002\n- **Environment variables:**\n  - `VITE_MOCK_MODE=false` (real mode, not mocked)\n  - `VITE_RPC_URL=http://127.0.0.1:8899` (local validator)\n  - `VITE_SOLANA_NETWORK=localnet`\n- **Timeouts:** 60s per test, 30s for server startup\n- **Browser:** Desktop Chrome, 1280x1080 viewport\n- **Traces:** Retained on failure for debugging\n\n---\n\n## **2. Smoke Test**\n\n**File:** `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/e2e/local/smoke.spec.ts`\n\nMinimal test that verifies:\n- App loads in real wallet mode against the local validator\n- Main title (`.rpg-title`) is visible\n- Wallet icon (`.rpg-wallet-icon`) is visible (disconnected state)\n- No critical console errors\n\n---\n\n## **3. Bootstrap & Teardown Scripts**\n\n**Bootstrap:** `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/scripts/localnet-bootstrap.sh`\n\nSteps:\n1. Preflight checks: ensures `coinflip.so`, `platform.so`, and keypairs exist (requires `anchor build` first)\n2. Checks `solana-test-validator` is available\n3. **Critical:** Verifies `io_uring` syscall support (Solana 3.x requirement — fails if `--security-opt=seccomp=unconfined` missing in Docker)\n4. Kills any existing validator on port 8899 or from `.localnet.pid`\n5. Cleans ledger directory for fresh state\n6. Starts `solana-test-validator` with both programs preloaded at genesis:\n   - Coinflip: `BdHFeqmkYe7znXV1Avk3zz496Pjo8QhEDN4MKPUTAWwx`\n   - Platform: `85qwC1cDpSYkBBHUcN4nuZ119hCx4N94X38GjAHxnWjA`\n7. Polls RPC health endpoint until ready (max 30s wait)\n8. Writes PID to `.localnet.pid`\n\n**Teardown:** `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/scripts/localnet-teardown.sh`\n\nSteps:\n1. Reads PID from `.localnet.pid` and gracefully stops validator (5s timeout, then SIGKILL)\n2. Kills any stray process on port 8899\n3. Removes `.localnet-ledger/` directory\n4. Optionally removes `.localnet-validator.log` (unless `--keep-logs` flag)\n5. Safe to call multiple times\n\n---\n\n## **4. E2E Fixtures & Test Organization**\n\n**Fixture file:** `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/e2e/fixtures.ts`\n\nProvides a `stablePage` fixture that deterministically stabilizes the browser environment:\n\n- **Deterministic randomness:** Seeds `Math.random()` and `crypto.getRandomValues()` with Mulberry32 PRNG (seed 42)\n- **Frozen time:** `Date.now()` returns fixed timestamp `1767225600000` (2026-01-01)\n- **Animation freezing:** Injects CSS disabling all animations/transitions (duration 0s)\n- **SVG SMIL pausing:** Calls `pauseAnimations()` on all SVG elements\n- **Network stabilization:** Waits for `document.fonts.ready` + 300ms settle time\n- **Console error collection:** Fails test if any console errors detected during execution\n\n**Visual regression tests use this fixture:**\n- `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/e2e/visual/routes.spec.ts` — screenshots of 12 routes (home, coinflip, crash, etc.)\n- `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/e2e/visual/states.spec.ts` — connected/disconnected wallet states + error toast placement\n\n**Real mode tests** (don't freeze randomness):\n- `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/e2e/real/startup.spec.ts`\n  - Verifies app loads without console errors\n  - Checks wallet icon renders in disconnected state with \"—\" balance\n  - Tests clicking wallet icon to trigger connect (graceful handling in headless mode)\n\n---\n\n## **5. TestWalletProvider (Real Wallet Mode for E2E)**\n\n**File:** `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/packages/wallet/src/test/TestWalletProvider.tsx`\n\nAllows E2E tests to sign real transactions against local test-validator without browser extension:\n\n**Props:**\n- `keypair: Keypair` — signing keypair (usually generated in test setup)\n- `rpcUrl?: string` — defaults to `http://127.0.0.1:8899` (localhost validator)\n- `autoConnect?: boolean` — auto-connects on mount (default: true)\n\n**Methods provided:**\n- `connect()` — verifies keypair works via `connection.getBalance(keypair.publicKey)`\n- `disconnect()` — logs out\n- `sendTransaction(tx)` — signs with keypair, sends via `sendAndConfirmTransaction`, returns signature\n- `signMessage(msg)` — returns deterministic signature (first 64 bytes of secret key)\n\n**Exposes:**\n- `connected`, `connecting` — state flags\n- `address`, `publicKey` — keypair's address\n- `isMock: false` — indicates this is real wallet, not mock\n\n**Unit test:** `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/packages/wallet/src/test/TestWalletProvider.test.tsx`\n- Mocks `Connection.getBalance()` to return 1 SOL for testing without real RPC\n- Verifies auto-connect and keypair exposure\n\n---\n\n## **6. Solana Test Patterns (Bankrun)**\n\n**Files:** \n- `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/solana/tests/platform.ts`\n- `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/solana/tests/coinflip.ts`\n\n**Pattern — Fund accounts at context creation:**\n\n```typescript\n// From coinflip.ts\nfunction fundedAccountData(lamports = 100 * LAMPORTS_PER_SOL) {\n  return {\n    lamports,\n    data: Buffer.alloc(0),\n    owner: SystemProgram.programId,\n    executable: false,\n  };\n}\n\n// Inject pre-funded accounts into context\nconst context = await startAnchor(\"./\", [], [\n  { address: opponent.publicKey, info: fundedAccountData() },\n  { address: treasury.publicKey, info: fundedAccountData() },\n  // ... mock VRF accounts\n]);\n```\n\n**Balance checking helper:**\n```typescript\nasync function getBalance(t: TestContext, pubkey: PublicKey): Promise<number> {\n  const account = await t.context.banksClient.getAccount(pubkey);\n  return account ? Number(account.lamports) : 0;\n}\n```\n\n**No `airdrop()` used in tests** — instead, accounts are pre-funded at context creation via `startAnchor(..., [], [{ address, info }])`\n\n**Account mutation pattern:**\n```typescript\nt.context.setAccount(pubkey, {\n  lamports,\n  data: Buffer.alloc(...),\n  owner: SystemProgram.programId,\n  executable: false,\n});\n```\n\n---\n\n## **7. Wallet Context & Hooks**\n\n**Type definitions:** `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/packages/wallet/src/types.ts`\n\n```typescript\nexport interface WalletContextValue extends WalletState {\n  connect: () => Promise<void>;\n  disconnect: () => Promise<void>;\n  sendTransaction: (transaction: Transaction) => Promise<string>;\n  signMessage: (message: Uint8Array) => Promise<Uint8Array>;\n  isMock?: boolean;\n  getBalance?: () => number;  // Mock mode only\n  getBalanceLamports?: () => number;  // Mock mode only\n  updateBalance?: (deltaLamports: number) => void;  // Mock mode only\n}\n```\n\n**Hook:** `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/packages/wallet/src/useWallet.ts`\n\nSimple context consumer with error if used outside provider:\n```typescript\nexport function useWallet(): WalletContextValue {\n  const context = useContext(WalletContext);\n  if (!context) throw new Error(\"useWallet must be used within a WalletProvider\");\n  return context;\n}\n```\n\n**Exported providers:**\n- `MockWalletProvider` — lightweight, no browser extension needed\n- `RealWalletProvider` — @solana/wallet-adapter-react (lazy-loaded)\n- `TestWalletProvider` — for E2E testing with injected keypair\n- `WalletProvider` — router that picks the right provider based on mode\n\n---\n\n## **8. Key Insights**\n\n1. **Local E2E requires pre-built programs:**\n   - Must run `anchor build` in `solana/` before bootstrap script\n   - Programs are preloaded at validator genesis (not deployed post-start)\n   - Script validates `.so` files exist; silently fails if they don't\n\n2. **Docker/devcontainer requirement:**\n   - io_uring syscall must be unblocked\n   - Add `\"runArgs\": [\"--security-opt=seccomp=unconfined\"]` to devcontainer.json if missing\n\n3. **Visual regression relies on deterministic seeding:**\n   - All randomness frozen at predictable values (Math.random, Date.now, SVG animations)\n   - Enables pixel-perfect screenshot diffs\n\n4. **TestWalletProvider bridges E2E and unit tests:**\n   - Real transaction signing (not mocked)\n   - Can work with local validator or devnet/mainnet (configurable RPC)\n   - Ideal for E2E workflows testing real Solana interactions\n\n5. **Bankrun tests (unit-level) don't use airdrop:**\n   - Pre-fund accounts at context creation time\n   - Use `setAccount()` to mutate state mid-test\n   - No async RPC calls; everything is in-memory\n\n6. **Bootstrap script is idempotent:**\n   - Kills existing validators, cleans stale PID files\n   - Safe to run multiple times (e.g., in CI or before each test suite)\n\n7. **Three test modes exist:**\n   - **Mock mode** (visual regression): lightweight, deterministic, no network\n   - **Real mode** (smoke test): actual wallet UI, no on-chain interaction expected\n   - **E2E with TestWalletProvider** (future): real txns against local validator\n\n---\n\n## **Files Explored**\n\nAll files read:\n\n1. `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/playwright.local.config.ts`\n2. `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/e2e/local/smoke.spec.ts`\n3. `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/e2e/fixtures.ts`\n4. `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sourc